          "indeterminacy": 0.1,
          "falsity": 0.02
        },
        {
          "text": "One engineer with prior PCI-DSS experience is non-negotiable for payment service",
          "truth": 0.85,
          "indeterminacy": 0.12,
          "falsity": 0.03
        },
        {
          "text": "Payment processing should be outsourced to third-party gateway rather than handled in-house (strong recommendation)",
